Document: RDPipelineRasterizationState
Path: godot/classes/class_rdpipelinerasterizationstate.rst
Summary: Defines the rasterization state for a render pipeline.

Inherits: Resource < Object

This class defines the rasterization state for a render pipeline. Rasterization is the process of determining which pixels on the screen are covered by a primitive (like a triangle) and what their color should be. This class allows you to configure various aspects of this process.
